914db750-41f9-42f7-961f-be2c39674e28	5009-630	Beal Rando 8mm Golden Dry Rope	When used in its single state, this is a light, compact security rope that's dynamic enough to absorb modest impacts. Beal® recommends it for easy snow routes with no difficult passages, glacier travel and ski touring. If used for climbing, double it up. This is a hybrid with UIAA test results passing it as a twin rope. Beal conducted their own tests as a single strand with 80kg weight.2 strands have a UIAA fall rating of 12.2 strands are rated to an impact force of 8.5kN.Golden Dry treatment makes both the sheath and the core water resistant.Beal plants a tree for every rope sold.	["Home", "All", "Climbing", "Rock climbing", "Ropes, cords and slings", "Dynamic climbing ropes", "Rando 8mm Golden Dry Rope"]	{"Type": ["Twin"], "Length": ["30m (30 Meter)", "20m (20)", "20m (20 Meter)"], "Weight": ["740g (20)", "740g (20 Meter)"], "Made in": ["Madagascar"], "Diameter": ["8mm"], "Ideal for": ["Rock climbing", "Snow and ice climbing"], "Linear weight": ["37g/m"], "Halfway pattern change": ["No"], "Static elongation\\n\\nIn controlled tests, a weight is suspended from the rope (not dropped). Higher numbers indicate stretchier ropes.": ["8%"], "Dynamic elongation\\n\\nMaximum elongation in the first UIAA test fall, where a weight is attached to the rope and then dropped. Higher numbers indicate stretchier ropes.": ["36%"], "Impact force\\n\\nThe amount of force, in kN, that the first UIAA fall puts on the falling object. Less impact force puts less force on the climber, belayer, and protection during a fall.": ["8.5kN"], "UIAA fall rating\\n\\nIndicates the number of consecutive falls a rope withstood during testing in a controlled environment. The number is for reference only, and does not indicate the number of falls a rope will withstand during actual use or over its lifespan.": ["12"], "Treatment\\n\\nDry ropes have a water-resistant treatment on both core and sheath. Dry (UIAA certified) ropes have both core and sheath treated, plus meet the UIAA Water Repellent standard by passing a stringent test where a soaked rope cannot absorb more than 5% of the rope's weight.": ["Dry"]}	{"low": ["https://cdn.mec.ca/medias/sys_master/high-res/high-res/8807252131870/5009630-YLW00.jpg?w=600&h=600&auto=format&q=60&fit=fill&bg=FFF", "https://cdn.mec.ca/medias/sys_master/high-res/high-res/8807251443742/5009630-PNK00.jpg?w=600&h=600&auto=format&q=60&fit=fill&bg=FFF", "https://cdn.mec.ca/medias/sys_master/high-res/high-res/8807252131870/5009630-YLW00.jpg?w=600&h=600&auto=format&q=60&fit=fill&bg=FFF", "https://cdn.mec.ca/medias/sys_master/high-res/high-res/8807251443742/5009630-PNK00.jpg?w=600&h=600&auto=format&q=60&fit=fill&bg=FFF"], "high": ["https://cdn.mec.ca/medias/sys_master/high-res/high-res/8807252131870/5009630-YLW00.jpg", "https://cdn.mec.ca/medias/sys_master/high-res/high-res/8807251443742/5009630-PNK00.jpg", "https://cdn.mec.ca/medias/sys_master/high-res/high-res/8807252131870/5009630-YLW00.jpg", "https://cdn.mec.ca/medias/sys_master/high-res/high-res/8807251443742/5009630-PNK00.jpg"]}	79.71	https://www.mec.ca/en/product/5009-630/Rando-8mm-Golden-Dry-Rope
