 the number of runs you do on a stellar ski day!": ["No"]}	{"low": ["https://cdn.mec.ca/medias/sys_master/high-res/high-res/8810402021406/5023114-BK000.jpg?w=600&h=600&auto=format&q=60&fit=fill&bg=FFF"], "high": ["https://cdn.mec.ca/medias/sys_master/high-res/high-res/8810402021406/5023114-BK000.jpg"]}	87.6	https://www.mec.ca/en/product/5023-114/Twin-Sensor-Watch
