43fd084e-427a-4f20-8e78-89dea352d26a	5018-587	DMM Belaymaster 2 Screwlock Carabiner	Ever looked down at your belay device to find the attached carabiner cross-loaded beween the rope and the belay loop? The Belay Master offers a significant safety improvement by offering a pivoting catch that locks down on the gate and keeps the carabiner properly aligned. In addition, it can only be engaged once the carabiner is locked, so it acts as great reminder. The carabiner is a nice medium size, with a large rope radius and soft angles.I-beam construction is strong and light.Clean nose prevents snagging on the belay loop or device.Screw gate must be manually engaged.Can be used without the catch, which twists off if you don’t want it.	["Home", "All", "Climbing", "Rock climbing", "Carabiners and draws", "Locking carabiners", "Belaymaster 2 Screwlock Carabiner"]	{"Weight": ["93g"], "Made in": ["United Kingdom"], "Material": ["Aluminum alloy"], "Gate type": ["Straight"], "Ideal for": ["Snow and ice climbing", "Rock climbing", "Indoor climbing"], "CE certified": ["Yes"], "Gate opening": ["2.0cm"], "Strength open": ["8kN"], "Strength closed": ["25kN"], "Three sigma tested": ["Yes"], "Strength cross-loaded": ["8kN"], "Lock type\\n\\nAuto-locking biners use a spring mechanism to close. Screwgate have a collar that you screw open or closed.": ["Screwgate"]}	{"low": ["https://cdn.mec.ca/medias/sys_master/high-res/high-res/8807123189790/5018587-NOC02.jpg?w=600&h=600&auto=format&q=60&fit=fill&bg=FFF", "https://cdn.mec.ca/medias/sys_master/high-res/high-res/8807123353630/5018587-NOC02-ALT-BACK.jpg?w=600&h=600&auto=format&q=60&fit=fill&bg=FFF", "https://cdn.mec.ca/medias/sys_master/high-res/high-res/8807123189790/5018587-NOC02.jpg?w=600&h=600&auto=format&q=60&fit=fill&bg=FFF", "https://cdn.mec.ca/medias/sys_master/high-res/high-res/8807123353630/5018587-NOC02-ALT-BACK.jpg?w=600&h=600&auto=format&q=60&fit=fill&bg=FFF"], "high": ["https://cdn.mec.ca/medias/sys_master/high-res/high-res/8807123189790/5018587-NOC02.jpg", "https://cdn.mec.ca/medias/sys_master/high-res/high-res/8807123353630/5018587-NOC02-ALT-BACK.jpg", "https://cdn.mec.ca/medias/sys_master/high-res/high-res/8807123189790/5018587-NOC02.jpg", "https://cdn.mec.ca/medias/sys_master/high-res/high-res/8807123353630/5018587-NOC02-ALT-BACK.jpg"]}	111.69	https://www.mec.ca/en/product/5018-587/Belaymaster-2-Screwlock-Carabiner
eb04fd6b-18ba-4391-8590-bcb3a8d30b6b	5017-917	DMM HB Alloy Offset Nuts	Son of the famed HB offsets and produced on modified HB dies, these nuts will find a home on intermediate to experienced climber's racks, for placing in flaring and shallow cracks.Made of heat-treated aluminum alloy to maximize strength and "bite".Colour-coded sizing with upside-down labels for easy ID on your harness.Tops are recessed to allow the wire to sit flush. Countersunk drill holes prevent stress points where the wire enters, and help protect the wire from wear.Tumbled to remove sharp edges that might hinder placements.Wires are matched to nut size, so they can be placed at full reach without flopping.Full size crimp used in wire for strength.Lightening holes in the larger sizes reduce weight.	["Home", "All", "Climbing", "Rock climbing", "Rock hardware", "Cams, nuts and hexes", "Nuts, hexes and nut tools", "HB Alloy Offset Nuts"]	{"Head": ["Aluminum"], "Stem": ["Double stainless steel"], "Range": ["10-12.2mm (7)", "10.5-14.2mm (8)", "13.6-16.8mm (9)", "16-19.8mm (10)", "17.6-23.4mm (11)"], "Weight": ["28g (7)", "30g (8)", "39g (9)", "46g (10)", "55g (11)"], "Made in": ["United Kingdom"], "Ideal for": ["Trad and aid climbing"], "CE certified": ["Yes"], "Three sigma tested": ["Yes"], "Strength\\n\\nThe maximum force generated by a fall the equipment can withstand. The range includes all sizes.": ["12kN"]}	{"low": ["https://cdn.mec.ca/medias/sys_master/high-res/high-res/8807204323358/5017917-NOC02.jpg?w=600&h=600&auto=format&q=60&fit=fill&bg=FFF", "https://cdn.mec.ca/medias/sys_master/high-res/high-res/8807204028446/5017917-NOC02-ALT-11.jpg?w=600&h=600&auto=format&q=60&fit=fill&bg=FFF", "https://cdn.mec.ca/medias/sys_master/high-res/high-res/8807204061214/5017917-NOC02-ALT-10.jpg?w=600&h=600&auto=format&q=60&fit=fill&bg=FFF", "https://cdn.mec.ca/medias/sys_master/high-res/high-res/8807204093982/5017917-NOC02-ALT-9.jpg?w=600&h=600&auto=format&q=60&fit=fill&bg=FFF", "https://cdn.mec.ca/medias