3dacff89-8343-44d8-bf02-562ee7991ac8	5024-601	Garmin BlueChart g3 Canada Micro SD/SD Card	Get the most from your Garmin GPS78 and other compatible units. This card comes preloaded with charts of Canada's east and west coasts as well as the Great Lakes. Realistic navigation features show everything from shaded depth contours and coastlines to spot soundings, navaids, port plans, wrecks, obstructions, intertidal zones, restricted areas, IALA symbols and more.Smooth display presentation includes seamless transitioning between zoom levels and more continuity across chart boundaries.Compatible with HomePort™ software that lets you use BlueChart data to conveniently plan and organize routes from your computer before your trip. (You need HomePort software in order to view charts on your Windows based computer.)	["Home", "All", "Camping and hiking", "Tools and accessories", "Maps and guidebooks", "Maps", "Digital maps", "BlueChart g3 Canada Micro SD/SD Card"]	{"Weight": ["4g"], "Made in": ["USA"], "Ideal for": ["Kayak touring", "Canoe tripping"]}	{"low": ["https://cdn.mec.ca/medias/sys_master/high-res/high-res/9049610158110/5024601-BK000.jpg?w=600&h=600&auto=format&q=60&fit=fill&bg=FFF", "https://cdn.mec.ca/medias/sys_master/high-res/high-res/8810672062494/5024601-BK000-ALT-DETAIL.jpg?w=600&h=600&auto=format&q=60&fit=fill&bg=FFF", "https://cdn.mec.ca/medias/sys_master/high-res/high-res/9049623592990/5024601-BK000-ALT-COUNTRY.jpg?w=600&h=600&auto=format&q=60&fit=fill&bg=FFF", "https://cdn.mec.ca/medias/sys_master/high-res/high-res/9049610158110/5024601-BK000.jpg?w=600&h=600&auto=format&q=60&fit=fill&bg=FFF", "https://cdn.mec.ca/medias/sys_master/high-res/high-res/8810672062494/5024601-BK000-ALT-DETAIL.jpg?w=600&h=600&auto=format&q=60&fit=fill&bg=FFF", "https://cdn.mec.ca/medias/sys_master/high-res/high-res/9049623592990/5024601-BK000-ALT-COUNTRY.jpg?w=600&h=600&auto=format&q=60&fit=fill&bg=FFF"], "high": ["https://cdn.mec.ca/medias/sys_master/high-res/high-res/9049610158110/