aaf3cd61-d5d8-45f2-bb6c-a0d648c8166d	5024-812	MEC Drencher Pants - Men's	Affordable pull-over pants for your daily commute. They’re slim enough not to flap in the wind, yet roomy enough to fit over your regular clothes. The fully waterproof construction makes them best suited to shorter, lower-intensity rides, where interior moisture build-up will be minimal.Very durable 100% nylon fabric with polyurethane coating for waterproofness.Fully seam-taped for maximum protection.DWR coating for improved comfort.Elasticized waist with drawcord.Small rise at waist back to keep you covered in the riding position.Subtly articulated knees for comfortable pedalling.Gusseted knee to ankle zipper for easier on and off.Velcro® ankle closures can cinch tight to stay out of the chain.Reflective strips on the leg and hip for visibility at night or in dull weather.\n\nRelaxed fit, Regular rise\n\n\n\nFit guide\n\nGarments, designed for specific activities have features that aren’t always adaptable to general use. For example, cycling clothing is longer in the back and arms. Activity aside, the fit of MEC clothing falls into these categories:\n\n\n\n\n\nOur next to skin fit that contours the body for no distractions\n\n\n\n\n\nOur close to body fit with a low profile silhouette for ease of movement\n\n\n\n\n\nOur standard, slightly off body fit for unrestricted comfort\n\n\n\n\n\nOur roomy, off body fit for maximum comfort and easy layering\n\n\nAll MEC men’s and boy’s pants are regular rise.\n\n\n\n\n        Sustainability\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nBluesign\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n                      Bluesign® Approved Material	["Home", "All", "Clothing", "Bottoms", "Pants", "Rain pants", "Drencher Pants"]	{"Type": ["Waterproof"], "Weight": ["284g (Medium)"], "Made in": ["China"], "Pockets": ["None"], "Ideal for": ["Cycle commuting", "Cycle touring"], "Face fabric": ["Nylon"], "Construction": ["Unlined"], "Additional feature(s)": ["Gusseted cuffs", "Reflective details"], "Product sustainabilit