908f5723-86f5-4db7-aa70-0041f98e852f	5005-817	Rivers of the Upper Ottawa Valley	Every year, thousands of canoe trippers paddle the Ottawa River and its tributaries. The area has rugged characteristics that whitewater paddlers crave, but it also has many waterways for novice or cautious paddlers. The author – who has decades of experience as a guide and wilderness tripper – outlines options for paddlers of all abilities. Areas covered include Ottawa Valley Northwest, Montreal River, Makobe River, Mattawa River, Petawawa River, Barron River, and many more.	["Home", "All", "Travel gear", "Books and maps", "Guidebooks", "Rivers of the Upper Ottawa Valley"]	{"ISBN": ["9781550464382"], "Pages": ["120"], "Author": ["Hap Wilson"], "Made in": ["Canada"], "Language": ["English"], "Ideal for": ["Canoeing", "Canoe tripping"], "Published": ["2004"], "Regionality": ["Ontario"]}	{"low": ["https://cdn.mec.ca/medias/sys_master/high-res/high-res/8815588343838/5005817-NOC02.jpg?w=600&h=600&auto=format&q=60&fit=fill&bg=FFF"], "high": ["https://cdn.mec.ca/medias/sys_master/high-res/high-res/8815588343838/5005817-NOC02.jpg"]}	24.85	https://www.mec.ca/en/product/5005-817/Rivers-of-the-Upper-Ottawa-Valley
4ce8c2e4-c6b9-4293-b8a3-5391b177d773	4000-338	Rocky Stretch Gore-Tex Oversocks - Unisex	Wear these versatile Gore-Tex® socks over your normal sock system and inside cycling shoes, boots, or light hikers to keep your socks and feet dry. Unlike footwear with built-in Gore-Tex liners, these socks allow you greater flexibility. You can benefit from the waterproofness of Gore-Tex when it’s wet out, and remove the socks to increase breathability in drier conditions. Plus, you can switch them among several pairs of footwear.Made of stretch Gore-Tex for waterproof breathability.Non-stretch sole and backstay for durability.	["Home", "All", "Footwear", "Socks", "Hiking socks", "Stretch Gore-Tex Oversocks"]	{"Weight": ["85g (9)"], "Made in": ["USA"], "Ideal for": ["Day hiking", "Backpacking", "Cycle commuting", "Cycle touring"], "Thickness": ["Thin"], "Cuff height": ["Mid-calf"], "Additional feature(s)": ["Waterproof"], "Anatomical fit\\n\\nLeft foot and right foot specific socks provide precise fit.": ["No"], "Cushioning\\n\\nLayers of cushioning, in some athletic socks, are knit in to reduce impact. Mapped socks are activity-specific and will offer cushioning in common pressure areas.": ["None"]}	{"low": ["https://cdn.mec.ca/medias/sys_master/high-res/high-res/8805597052958/4000338-BK000.jpg?w=600&h=600&auto=format&q=60&fit=fill&bg=FFF"], "high": ["https://cdn.mec.ca/medias/sys_master/high-res/high-res/8805597052958/4000338-BK000.jpg"]}	224.51	https://www.mec.ca/en/product/4000-338/Stretch-Gore-Tex-Oversocks
