6e8d0b5a-ed1c-4959-afa8-976ca395a18c	5010-681	Western Mountaineering Bristlecone MF -23C Winter Down Sleeping Bag - Unisex	No cold can turn you away when you're hunkered down in your Bristlecone. It's built big and is filled with down, to yield 20cm of simmering loft to keeps you heated.  A large draft tube and down filled collar make certain that winter remains outside. With 2 zippers, it can be zipped to other Western Mountaineering mummy bags or unzipped to lie flat.Shell is weather-resistant MicroLite XP™ microfibre. While extremely weather resistant, MicroLite XP retains excellent breathability to prevent your bag from wetting out.Semi-rectangular shape with a full collar and insulated hood.Insulated with goose down.15cm spacing, sideblock baffle construction.2 #5 YKK locking zippers.	["Home", "All", "Camping and hiking", "Sleeping bags, sleeping pads, quilts and pillows", "Sleeping bags", "Bristlecone MF -23C Winter Down Sleeping Bag"]	{"Shape": ["Mummy"], "Length": ["Regular fits to 6' 0\\" (183 cm)", "Long fits to 6' 6\\" (198 cm)"], "Weight": ["1.79kg (Regular Left Zip)", "1.9kg (Long Left Zip)"], "Made in": ["USA"], "Seasons": ["Winter (-15°C to -40°C)"], "Hip girth": ["155cm"], "Ideal for": ["Winter and expedition camping"], "Foot girth": ["122cm"], "Insulation": ["850+ fill-power goose down"], "Packed size": ["25 x 50cm"], "Temperature": ["-23°C"], "Construction": ["Baffle"], "Shoulder girth": ["175cm"], "Additional feature(s)": ["Draft tube behind zipper", "DWR-treated shell fabric", "Stuff sack included"], "Yoke\\n\\nAn insulated collar that covers yours neck and shoulders to reduce heat loss.": ["No"], "Capacity\\n\\nThe number of average sized people that the product can comfortably sleep.": ["1-person"], "Loft\\n\\nThe thickness or puffiness of a bag – a key factor in determing a bag's warmth.": ["20cm"], "Down weight\\n\\nThe amount of down used to fill the product (measured in grams and given for size medium bags).": ["1190g"]}	{"low": ["https://c