9222549d-c050-4f15-9329-1982d2b8ffbc	5018-693	Western Mountaineering Puma Microfibre -32C Winter Down Sleeping Bag - Unisex	Mega warmth and big, puffy loft, in a bag weighs only 1.6kg. Insulated with high-lofting goose down, it's ideal for ski touring, and winter mountaineering. 2 densely-packed interlocking draft tubes and a down-filled collar seal out biting cold air. Its V-block side baffle gives you amazing down control, which is key in a bag with this much loft. MicroLite XP™ shell is breathable yet extremely weather-resistant.MicroLite XP shell.Insulated with goose down.Side baffles with15cm spacing.Interlocking draft tubes.	["Home", "All", "Camping and hiking", "Sleeping bags, sleeping pads, quilts and pillows", "Sleeping bags", "Puma Microfibre -32C Winter Down Sleeping Bag"]	{"Shape": ["Mummy"], "Length": ["Small fits to 5' 6\\" (168 cm)", "Regular fits to 6' 0\\" (183 cm)", "Long fits to 6' 6\\" (198 cm)"], "Weight": ["1.48kg (Small Left Zip)", "1.56kg (Regular Left Zip)", "1.65kg (Long Left Zip)"], "Made in": ["USA"], "Seasons": ["Winter (-15°C to -40°C)"], "Hip girth": ["142cm"], "Ideal for": ["Winter and expedition camping"], "Foot girth": ["99cm"], "Insulation": ["850+ fill-power goose down"], "Packed size": ["25 x 50cm"], "Temperature": ["-32°C"], "Construction": ["Baffle"], "Shoulder girth": ["163cm"], "Additional feature(s)": ["DWR-treated shell fabric", "Stuff sack included", "Ultralight"], "Yoke\\n\\nAn insulated collar that covers yours neck and shoulders to reduce heat loss.": ["Yes"], "Capacity\\n\\nThe number of average sized people that the product can comfortably sleep.": ["1-person"], "Loft\\n\\nThe thickness or puffiness of a bag – a key factor in determing a bag's warmth.": ["23cm"], "Down weight\\n\\nThe amount of down used to fill the product (measured in grams and given for size medium bags).": ["1020g"]}	{"low": ["https://cdn.mec.ca/medias/sys_master/high-res/high-res/8964025942046/5018693-LBL00.jpg?w=600&h=600&auto=format&q=60&fit=fi