986b2d9f-68b7-4861-a6ec-4f581ea07f14	5002-357	Western Mountaineering Ultralite -7C Down Sleeping Bag - Unisex	Ideal for cycling trips across varying climate zones and extended 3-season backpacking. Incredibly light and compressible, it's designed for thru hikers, climbers or other light and fast aficionados. The compromise for all its lightness is the durability of the shell and lining fabric. It's an ultralight, high-performance bag, not one for kicking-around or putting into continuous use, but treat it nicely and you'll be sleeping warm season after season.Shell and lining are incredibly light and compressible sub 20-denier ripstop nylon.Down-filled draft collar seals in warm air and eliminate drafts around the shoulders and neck.Continuous baffle construction (no sideblock baffle) and 5¼in. baffle spacing offers down control and minimizes cold spots.Narrow profile offers a close fit for maximum heat efficiency.#5 YKK zipper.Dimensions provide room to sleep comfortably, but not enough to sprawl.	["Home", "All", "Camping and hiking", "Sleeping bags, sleeping pads, quilts and pillows", "Sleeping bags", "Ultralite -7C Down Sleeping Bag"]	{"Shape": ["Mummy"], "Length": ["Small fits to 5' 6\\" (168 cm)", "Regular fits to 6' 0\\" (183 cm)", "Long fits to 6' 6\\" (198 cm)"], "Weight": ["795g (Small Left Zip)", "820g (Regular Left Zip)", "880g (Long Left Zip)"], "Made in": ["USA"], "Seasons": ["3-season (-2°C to -12°C)"], "Hip girth": ["130cm"], "Ideal for": ["Backpacking"], "Foot girth": ["97cm"], "Insulation": ["850+ fill-power goose down"], "Face fabric": ["15-denier nylon"], "Packed size": ["18 x 33cm"], "Temperature": ["-7°C"], "Construction": ["Baffle"], "Lining/backer": ["15-denier nylon"], "Shoulder girth": ["150cm"], "Additional feature(s)": ["Stuff sack included", "Ultralight"], "Recommended Compression Sack": ["12L"], "Yoke\\n\\nAn insulated collar that covers yours neck and shoulders to reduce heat loss.": ["Yes"], "Capacity\\n\\nThe number of average sized p