40a1e142-99a8-4976-8654-2758a2cc42a1	5027-775	Wild Country Ropeman 2 Ascender	The Ropeman 2 makes a great alternative to prusiks or heavier ascenders. It is essentially an incomplete ascender until you add a locking carabiner to it. The carabiner acts as the spine against which the cam presses the rope. The version has a steel cam and forged side plates. It's a touch lighter than earlier versions, and the internal radii gives it smoother function with different types of carabiners and skinny cords.Stainless steel cam, aluminum side plates.Forged side plates work with a range of carabiner types and shapes.Works with ropes from 8 to 13mm.4kN strength.CE certified.	["Home", "All", "Climbing", "Rock climbing", "Uppers and downers", "Ascenders", "Ropeman 2 Ascender"]	{"Weight": ["92g"], "Made in": ["Taiwan"], "Ideal for": ["Snow and ice climbing", "Trad and aid climbing"], "CE certified": ["Yes"], "Cam material": ["Stainless steel"], "Body material": ["Aluminum"], "Rope diameter\\n\\nThe maximum diameter or the range of rope diameter that is compatible with the device.": ["8 - 13mm"]}	{"low": ["https://cdn.mec.ca/medias/sys_master/high-res/high-res/8807216054302/5027775-GLD00.jpg?w=600&h=600&auto=format&q=60&fit=fill&bg=FFF", "https://cdn.mec.ca/medias/sys_master/high-res/high-res/8807215923230/5027775-GLD00-ALT-ONROPE.jpg?w=600&h=600&auto=format&q=60&fit=fill&bg=FFF", "https://cdn.mec.ca/medias/sys_master/high-res/high-res/8807216054302/5027775-GLD00.jpg?w=600&h=600&auto=format&q=60&fit=fill&bg=FFF", "https://cdn.mec.ca/medias/sys_master/high-res/high-res/8807215923230/5027775-GLD00-ALT-ONROPE.jpg?w=600&h=600&auto=format&q=60&fit=fill&bg=FFF"], "high": ["https://cdn.mec.ca/medias/sys_master/high-res/high-res/8807216054302/5027775-GLD00.jpg", "https://cdn.mec.ca/medias/sys_master/high-res/high-res/8807215923230/5027775-GLD00-ALT-ONROPE.jpg", "https://cdn.mec.ca/medias/sys_master/high-res/high-res/8807216054302/5027775-GLD00.jpg", "https://cdn.mec.ca/medias/sys_master/hig