59045f01-ae39-40c8-b7b3-b885fdcc6c0a	4003-970	Zotefoams Blue Foam Long Sleeping Pad - Unisex	Not all blue foam is created equal – the exceptional nine percent EVA content makes this stuff stronger than most foam on the market. Not as durable as Evazote®, this pad still has good insulation and flexibility.Dimensions are 190 x 50cm.	["Home", "All", "Camping and hiking", "Sleeping bags, sleeping pads, quilts and pillows", "Sleeping pads", "Closed-cell foam sleeping pads", "Blue Foam Long Sleeping Pad"]	{"Type": ["Foam pad"], "Shape": ["Rectangle"], "Width": ["50cm"], "Length": ["190cm"], "Weight": ["275g"], "Made in": ["Canada"], "Ideal for": ["Backpacking", "Winter and expedition camping"], "Thickness": ["1cm"], "Insulation": ["Closed-cell foam"], "Rolled length": ["53cm"], "Rolled diameter": ["16cm"], "Additional feature(s)": ["Ultralight"], "Capacity\\n\\nThe number of average sized people that the product can comfortably sleep.": ["1-person"], "R value (thermal resistance)\\n\\nMeasures insulative value. Higher values indicate more warmth: 1 to 3 are best for warm weather. 3 to 4 are best for 3-season use.4.5 or higher is best for winter.": ["1.4"]}	{"low": ["https://cdn.mec.ca/medias/sys_master/high-res/high-res/8816477405214/4003970-NOC02.jpg?w=600&h=600&auto=format&q=60&fit=fill&bg=FFF"], "high": ["https://cdn.mec.ca/medias/sys_master/high-res/high-res/8816477405214/4003970-NOC02.jpg"]}	455.33	https://www.mec.ca/en/product/4003-970/Blue-Foam-Long-Sleeping-Pad
