3dd52def-ad0c-495a-a26e-3ffe900a5565	0808-097	Zotefoams Evazote Bivy Sleeping Pad - Unisex	This 5-millimetre thick foam pad has good resiliency thanks to its high 18 percent EVA content. Its smaller size makes it a good choice for surprise bivies. Evazote® pads are physically blown with pure nitrogen gas for durability. Flexible to –70 degrees Celsius, it’s also abrasion and UV resistant.Dimensions are 150 x 50cm	["Home", "All", "Camping and hiking", "Sleeping bags, sleeping pads, quilts and pillows", "Sleeping pads", "Closed-cell foam sleeping pads", "Evazote Bivy Sleeping Pad"]	{"Type": ["Foam pad"], "Shape": ["Rectangle"], "Width": ["50cm"], "Length": ["150cm"], "Weight": ["175g"], "Made in": ["Canada"], "Ideal for": ["Winter and expedition camping", "Backpacking"], "Thickness": ["0.5cm"], "Insulation": ["Closed-cell foam"], "Rolled length": ["51cm"], "Rolled diameter": ["10cm"], "Additional feature(s)": ["Ultralight"], "Capacity\\n\\nThe number of average sized people that the product can comfortably sleep.": ["1-person"], "R value (thermal resistance)\\n\\nMeasures insulative value. Higher values indicate more warmth: 1 to 3 are best for warm weather. 3 to 4 are best for 3-season use.4.5 or higher is best for winter.": ["0.7"]}	{"low": ["https://cdn.mec.ca/medias/sys_master/high-res/high-res/8816476323870/0808097-NOC02.jpg?w=600&h=600&auto=format&q=60&fit=fill&bg=FFF"], "high": ["https://cdn.mec.ca/medias/sys_master/high-res/high-res/8816476323870/0808097-NOC02.jpg"]}	461.95	https://www.mec.ca/en/product/0808-097/Evazote-Bivy-Sleeping-Pad
